### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Mise à jour complète (cas nominal)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/update-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "title": "Nouveau titre",
  "event_date": "2024-12-26T18:00:00Z",
  "guest_count": 200,
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### Test 2 - Mise à jour partielle
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/update-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "title": "Titre modifié"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: event_id manquant
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/update-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Nouveau titre"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: événement terminé
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/update-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "completed-event-uuid",
  "title": "Titre modifié"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: statut invalide
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/update-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "status": "invalid_status"
}

